# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.  
This project follows [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/).

---

## [1.0.0] - 2025-08-20
### Added
- Initial release of **Ammamma Kathalu** app.
- User authentication (Sign up / Login).
- Traditional Mode (text & audio).
- Meme Mode (images & videos).
- Profile management, settings, and logout options.
- Admin access for managing content.
- Offline/low-network compatibility.
- Mobile-friendly layout with responsive UI.

---

## [1.1.0] - Upcoming
### Planned
- Improved audio/video storage with cloud integration.
- Dark/light theme toggle.
- Multi-language support (starting with Telugu + English).
- Search and filter options for content.

